nimbus new vault.toml
(registers a vault from vault.toml; see README.md for the config format)

nimbus vaults
(prints registered vault names)

nimbus select my-vault
nimbus ls
(lists my-vault's current directory)

nimbus cd docs
nimbus put ./notes.txt
(copies ./notes.txt from the local vault into my-vault:/docs)

nimbus get notes.txt ./downloads
(copies my-vault:/docs/notes.txt out to ./downloads)

See README.md for the full command reference.
